data.description: This home feels like it's brand new! The open-design floor plan features a beautifully maintained interior and features large family room that flows through the dining room area and kitchen. The kitchen offers plenty of storage space, a separate walk-in pantry, and a versatile extra storage room. The primary bedroom is huge and provides a large walk-in closet and beautiful ensuite bathroom. Pristine well-maintained home. Enjoy the expansive backyard that comes complete with a slab patio and lawn with automatic sprinklers. The property sits on a highly-desired interior lot which provides a huge backyard area. Perfectly situated in an incomparable Heartland master-planned community. The community offers several amenities such as walking and biking trails, parks, a lake with a fishing pier, parks, playgrounds, and a gym. Every convenience is a short distance away. Highly sought after school district.
